:: Start
You wake up in a dim room.

(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[Everything feels soft and blurry at the edges.]]

(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[...your bed, the ceiling, the pale rectangle of the window.]]

(after: 4.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You probably had a bad dream but you can't recall it.]]

(after: 6s)[(transition:"dissolve")[[[Stay a little longer...|Wake Up Call]]]]

(after: 7.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[[[Get up]]]]

:: Wake Up Call
You stare at the ceiling.

(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You do remember that tomorrow is the last day of school.]]

(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[All your friends seem to know exactly where they're going.]]

(after: 4.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You don't exactly have a plan but there's no way you're staying in this small town for much longer.]]

(after: 6s)[(transition:"dissolve")[[[Get up]]]]

(after: 7.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[[[Go back to sleep|Go Back To Sleep]]]]

:: Go Back To Sleep
(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[[[Wake up|Start]]]]

:: Get up
Your feet find the floor. The room is dim and blurry.

(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[[[Look out the window]]]]

(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[[[Find your glasses]]]]

:: Look out the window
(if: $hasGlasses is true)[
(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[The street is still and dark. Two German cars are parked at the curb. A set of cypress trees are swaying slightly.]]

(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You can hear some crickets chirping in the distance.]]

(after: 4.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[Nothing is happening. Everything is exactly as it always has been.]]

(after: 6s)[(transition:"dissolve")[[[Go for a walk]]]]
]
(else:)[
(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[Outside is a smear of dark blue and grey. Trees, maybe. The street. It's hard to tell where one thing ends and another begins.]]

(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[[[Find your glasses]]]]
]

:: Find your glasses
(set: $hasGlasses to true)
You feel along the nightstand until your fingers close around the familiar frames. You put them on.

(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[The room snaps into focus. Posters, clothes on the chair, and the stack of half-packed boxes in the corner.]]

(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[A documentary about submarines is playing on mute on your small tube television.]]

(after: 4.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[[[Look out the window]]]]

:: Go for a walk
(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You find yourself on the road outside your house. It's still dark.]]

(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[The air is cool and quiet.]]

(after: 4.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[The neighborhood is completely still.]]

(after: 6s)[(transition:"dissolve")[
[[Walk south toward the cave →|Cave]]
[[Head east to the garage →|Garage]]
[[Cut across to the neighbor's shack →|Neighbor's Shack]]
]]

:: Garage
(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[The garage door is unlocked. It swings open with a sound like a held breath.]]

(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[Inside: old paint cans, a broken lawnmower, your dad's tools hanging in their outlines on the pegboard.]]

(after: 4.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[On the workbench you spot a pocket flashlight.]]

(if: $hasFlashlight is false)[
(after: 6s)[(transition:"dissolve")[[[Pick up the flashlight →|Take Flashlight]]]]]
(else:)[
(after: 6s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You already have the flashlight. Everything else seems useless for your journey.

[[Head back outside →|Go for a walk]]]]]

:: Take Flashlight
(set: $hasFlashlight to true)
The flashlight is cold and solid in your hand. You click it on. A beam cuts through the dark.

(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[[[Head back outside →|Go for a walk]]]]

:: Take Wand
(set: $hasWand to true)
You pick it up. It's lighter than it looks. The warmth travels up your fingers, into your wrist. You pocket it without thinking too hard about it.

(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[[[Head back outside →|Go for a walk]]]]

:: Cave
(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You don't remember there being a cave here.]]

(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[And yet here it is: a low mouth in the hillside at the end of the street, half hidden behind the Peters' fence. Dark inside.]]

(after: 4.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[Something drips somewhere in the dark.]]

(after: 6s)[(transition:"dissolve")[
(if: $hasFlashlight is true)[
(if: $knowsCaveSecret is true)[[[Shine your flashlight inside →|Cave Inside]]]
(else:)[//You step inside but the passages twist and repeat. After a while you find yourself back at the entrance. You need to know the way.//

[[Back to the street →|Go for a walk]]]
]
(else:)[//It's too dark to see anything. You'd need a light.//

[[Back to the street →|Go for a walk]]]
]]

:: Neighbor's Shack
(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[The path to the shack runs along the ditch. Tall grass on both sides, wet with dew.]]

(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[Then you hear it. A toad, somewhere in the grass. A slow, rhythmic ribbiting that somehow sounds almost intentional. Like it's saying something in a language just beyond reach.]]

(after: 4.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[The shack is dark. No lights on.]]

(after: 6s)[(transition:"dissolve")[
[[Listen to the toad →|Toad Song]]
[[Knock on the shack door →|Shack Door]]
[[Head back →|Go for a walk]]
]]

:: Shack Door
(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[The shack's door is unlocked and opens as you knock on it. It's a small town after all...]]

(if: $hasFlashlight is false)[
(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[//It's too dark to see anything inside.//]]
(after: 4.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[[[Back to the street →|Go for a walk]]]]]

(else:)[
(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You sweep the flashlight around. Among some gardening tools you spot a thin wooden stick. It's smooth and slightly warm to the touch.]]
(after: 4.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[It has a small crack running down one side that seems to glow, faintly, if you look at it from the corner of your eye.]]
(after: 6s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You're pretty sure that's an old back-scratcher.]]
(after: 7.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[Probably...]]
(if: $hasWand is false)[
(after: 9s)[(transition:"dissolve")[[[Pick up the stick →|Take Wand]]]]]
(else:)[
(after: 9s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You already picked up the wooden stick. Everything else seems useless for your journey.
[[Head back outside →|Go for a walk]]]]]
]

:: Toad Song
(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You crouch down in the wet grass and listen.]]

(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[At first it's just sound. Repetitive, ancient, amphibian.]]

(after: 4.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[But then... something shifts. Like tuning into a frequency. The ribbiting starts to resolve into something almost like syllables. Almost like your name.]]

(after: 6s)[(transition:"dissolve")[The grass around you begins to glow, very faintly. Pale green. Bioluminescent. Each blade lit from within.]]

(after: 7.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You sit there for a long time. You feel....]]

(after: 9s)[(transition:"dissolve")[weird.]]

(if: $hasWand is true)[
(after: 10.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[[[Touch the toad with the wooden stick →|Touch Toad]]]]]
(else:)[
(after: 10.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You have no idea what the toad wants to tell you. But you'd really like to know.

[[Stand up and continue →|Neighbor's Shack]]]]]

:: Touch Toad
(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You hesitate, then slowly reach out and touch the toad with the warm wooden stick.]]

(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[The glow surges. The ribbiting stops.]]

(after: 4.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[The toad looks at you with one enormous golden eye and says, very clearly:]]

(after: 6s)[(transition:"dissolve")[//"Left. Always left."//]]

(after: 7.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[It keeps staring you in the eyes.]]

(after: 9s)[(transition:"dissolve")[
(set: $knowsCaveSecret to true)
[[Stand up and head back →|Go for a walk]]
[[Take the toad with you →|Take Toad]]
]]

:: Take Toad
(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You carefully lift the toad up with both your hands.]]

(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[It's slippery but doesn't try to jump away. It stares you in the eyes, full of anticipation for your joint adventures.]]

(after: 4.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[After all, why shouldn't you keep it?]]

(after: 6s)[(transition:"dissolve")[Might come in handy.]]

(after: 7.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[
<pre>
