(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You remember that on your left hand the thumb is on the right.]]

(after: 4.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You are not confused anymore. You remember what the toad told you.]]

(after: 6s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You should head east.]]

(after: 7.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[Also, you really should remember to stop biting your nails.]]

(after: 9s)[(transition:"dissolve")[[[Back to the cave →|Cave Inside]]]]

