:: Light Cave
(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You arrive at a glittering cavern. The crystals catch your flashlight and scatter it across the walls in a thousand directions.]]
(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[It's beautiful.]]
(if: $hasToad is true)[
(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[Suddenly the toad in your pocket starts ribbiting nervously.]]
