:: Toad Advice
(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[//"Life will be rough. There are going to be tough times."//]]

(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[//"But you should never forget to enjoy yourself a little."//]]

(after: 4.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[The toad pauses, then blinks its enormous golden eye.]]

(after: 6s)[(transition:"dissolve")[//"How about you lick my head and forget about the future for a minute?"//]]

(after: 7.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[
[[Trust the toad. Lick it. →|Lick Toad]]
[[Go back to bed and forget what happened →|End1]]
]]

:: Lick Toad
(after: 1.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[Maybe the toad is right. Maybe you shouldn't worry too much for once.]]

(after: 3s)[(transition:"dissolve")[You bow your head, stick out your tongue, and gently lick the toad's head.]]

(after: 4.5s)[(transition:"dissolve")[The taste is overwhelming and bitter...]]
(after: 6s)[(transition:"dissolve")[...but almost instantly, the cave around you disappears.]]
